name: Fox Cute Acrylic Fashion Necklace
description:
This cute fox acrylic necklace is very on trend at the moment, the perfect gift for a child, teenager or fashion conscious adult!

The necklace comes on a personalised Hoobynoo World postcard with the fox's unique character profile on the back. The necklace is then wrapped in tissue paper and decorated ribbon.

My original illustration is printed directly onto the white plastic meaning it won't scratch or wear off. The pendant is hung on a 50cms (20") metal bronze coloured ball chain, the chain is secured with a standard lobster clasp.
Dimensions:

This acrylic fox pendant measures 3cms wide and 4cms high and is 3mm thick.
--------------------------------------
Freddie the Fox
Age: 2
Likes: Rooting through people’s rubbish
Dislikes: Vixens

Freddie is the cutest fox in all of Hoobynoo World. Unfortunately, he’s always covered in rubbish so very few animals get to see him in all his natural glory. Freddie doesn’t care what he looks like, but he is always extra careful to poke the bins before he roots in them: he once woke a sleeping vixen and got more than he bargained for!

name: Flamingo Acrylic Fashion Necklace
description:
This flamingo necklace would make an ideal gift for any occasion for those who love colourful statement jewellery! The unique character profile on the presentation card make this so much more than your average accessory.

The acrylic pendant measures 4.cms high and 2.5cms at the widest point and is 3mm thick. My illustration is printed directly onto the white plastic meaning it won't scratch or wear off. The pendant is presented on a 50cms (20") Hot Pink coloured ball chain, the chain is secured with a standard lobster clasp.

Each necklace comes presented on a personalised Hoobynoo World postcard with the characters unique profile on the back. The necklace is then lovingly wrapped in tissue paper and decorated with a rainbow coloured ribbon before being posted to you.
-------------------------------------------------------
Florence the Flamingo

Age: 7
Likes: Butterflies and Tiny fish
Dislikes: The colour pink

Florence is a rather unusual flamingo, mainly because she doesn’t like wading. Florence will do practically anything to avoid being partly submerged in water, and has even built a small raft so that she can float down the rivers and attempt to catch the fish in passing.

name: Cute Cupcake Acrylic Necklace
description:
This cute cupcake necklace would make an ideal gift for children, teenagers and those that love quirky jewellery.

The cupcake pendant measures 2.5cms x 3.8cms and is 3mm thick.

My illustration is printed directly onto the white plastic meaning it won't scratch or wear off. The pendant is hung on a 50cms (20") metal hot pink coloured ball chain, the chain is secured with a standard lobster clasp.

Each necklace comes presented on a personalised Hoobynoo World postcard with the characters unique profile on the back. The necklace is then lovingly wrapped in tissue paper and decorated with a rainbow coloured ribbon before being posted to you.

CELEBRITY ITEM
As worn by Lateysha Grace and Nicole Morris in Season 2 of MTV's The Valleys.
-------------------------------------------------------
Clarissa the Cupcake

Likes: Coloured sprinkles and gingerbread men
Dislikes: Hot ovens

Clarissa is the most popular of the Hoobynoo cupcakes, known for her pink frosting and multi-coloured sprinkles. Her best friend is Billy the Banana. When Hoobynoo supermarket closes, she can often be found in the vegetable aisle, playing snap with Billy and the other fruits.

name: Kawaii Rainbow Acrylic Necklace
description:
This super cute rainbow necklace would make the perfect gift for children, teenagers and adults who love quirky original jewellery.

This cute acrylic rainbow pendant measures 3.5cm x 2.5cm and is 3mm thick.

My unique illustration is digitally printed directly onto the white plastic meaning it won't scratch or wear off, the design is then laser cut for the perfect finish. The pendant is hung on a 45cm (18") metal silver coloured ball chain, the chain is secured with a standard lobster clasp.

Each necklace comes presented on a personalised Hoobynoo World postcard with the characters unique profile on the back.
 The necklace is then lovingly wrapped in tissue paper and decorated with a rainbow coloured ribbon before being posted to you.
------------------------------------------
Rihanna the Rainbow

Age: 32 mins (approx)
Likes: Leprechauns and pots of gold
Dislikes: Being seen

Rihanna is a very shy rainbow, and really doesn’t like being looked at by people. She is a very long and extremely bendy, translucent bow of shimmering, glimmering beauty and – sadly – she doesn’t hang around for very long. If you’re fortunate enough to glimpse her, run like the wind to catch her before she vanishes!
